    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Colorless, heavy, sweet liquid derived from natural fats and oils.  It can be used as a plasticizer in certain media.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
